{"tid":1146330,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"声优悠木碧开展同人社团活动！参与少年偶像广播剧制作","createTime":"2019-05-09T07:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T12:42:57.000Z","uid":43041,"like":2,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7204b31fb27ddb605659da5fcc692b3ce5ebb5ac","tid":1146330,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:31:42.000Z","msg":"在昨天，声优悠木碧通过推特宣布将有重大发表。虽然很多网友凑热闹问是不是结婚，不过悠木碧吐槽称不要随便被结婚呀！这次是自己迈出新的一步的通知。<br />\n<br />\n目前，这次的重大发表内容已经公开了。根据推特内容，这次悠木碧将要与声优丸山有香一起，进行同人广播剧CD企划&ldquo;idol_showtime&rdquo;的制作。作品预计将于2019年夏推出。<br />\n&ldquo;idol_showtime&rdquo;是以女性声优配音的少年音为主题的少年偶像广播剧CD企划。角色原案、剧本、音乐制作等都和声优有所关联。其中悠木碧负责剧本，并协助角色原案的设计。而负责配音的声优包括了田村睦心、斋贺光希、小林由美子、白石凉子、森奈奈子、小岩井小鸟和皆川纯子等。"},{"pid":"c1ae553be0d2ba90b04c2fee5eb07143641fbce1","tid":1146330,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sDkLfsZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsDkLfsZ.png&h=97baf662&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acef4d4570a5ed3e509994e8ed404c156acbc740","tid":1146330,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca102c9459d0c18483abd353503ca5d1e1e5f0f","tid":1146330,"uid":130225,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:37:51.000Z","msg":"屌你老母呀支那殘體狗"},{"pid":"e27668445fdb53486303712786cd2ad4d2af1428","tid":1146330,"uid":43041,"like":3,"dislike":39,"score":-36,"quote":{"pid":"8ca102c9459d0c18483abd353503ca5d1e1e5f0f","tid":1146330,"uid":130225,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:37:51.000Z","msg":"屌你老母呀支那殘體狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:39:07.000Z","msg":"躝啦屌你老母，死傻鳩又入我地動漫台踩場<br />\n祝你全家cancer死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets